OL,3,CMan charged with assisting synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker on earlier reconnaissance
OL,6,FAn 'associate' of Manchester synagogue
OL,7,Fattacker Jihad Al-Shamie has been
OL,8,Fcharged with helping him to carry out
OL,9,Freconnaissance at a UK defence
OL,10,Ffacility.
OL,12,FMohammed Bashir, 31, faces four
OL,13,Foffences, including preparation for
OL,14,Facts of terrorism where it is alleged
OL,15,Fhe drove Al-Shamie to an unnamed
OL,16,Fdefence facility on 14 August.
OL,18,FThe assistance provided was not in
OL,19,Frelation to the attack on the Heaton
OL,20,FPark Synagogue on 2 October, the Crown
OL,21,FProsecution Service (CPS) said.
