OL,3,CMan charged with assisting synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker on earlier reconnaissance
OL,6,FWorshippers Melvin Cravitz and Adrian
OL,7,FDaulby were killed after 35-year-old
OL,8,FAl-Shamie, a Syrian-born UK citizen,
OL,9,Fdrove his Kia Picanto into the gates
OL,10,Fof the synagogue and then began
OL,11,Fattacking with a knife, wearing a fake
OL,12,Fsuicide belt.
OL,14,FBashir, a British national whose self-
OL,15,Fdefined ethnicity is British
OL,16,FPakistani, has been released without
OL,17,Fcharge in relation to the attack,
OL,18,FCounter Terrorism Policing North West
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
