OL,3,CMan charged with assisting synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker on earlier reconnaissance
OL,6,FHe will also be prosecuted for sharing
OL,7,Fmaterial online with intent to
OL,8,Fencourage acts of terrorism, the CPS
OL,9,Fadded.
OL,11,FFrank Ferguson, chief crown prosecutor
OL,12,Fof the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,13,FSpecial Crime and Counter Terrorism
OL,14,FDivision, said: "Today, we have
OL,15,Fdecided to prosecute Mohammad Bashir
OL,16,Fwith terrorism offences - following a
OL,17,FCounter Terrorism Policing North West
OL,18,Finvestigation into his conduct linked
OL,19,Fto Jihad Al Shamie.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
