OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1764933450
OL,3,CMan charged with assisting synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker on earlier reconnaissance
OL,6,F"Our prosecutors have concluded that
OL,7,Fthere is sufficient evidence to charge
OL,8,FMohammad Bashir with one offence of
OL,9,Fpreparation of terrorist acts and
OL,10,Fthree offences of sharing terrorist
OL,11,Fpublications with Al-Shamie and others
OL,12,Fwith the intent to encourage acts of
OL,13,Fterrorism.
OL,15,F"We have worked closely with Counter
OL,16,FTerrorism Policing North West as they
OL,17,Fcarried out their investigation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUyD@aO]
