OL,3,CMan charged with assisting synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker on earlier reconnaissance
OL,6,FBashir will appear at Westminster
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on 5 December after
OL,8,Fbeing arrested at Manchester Airport
OL,9,Fon 27 November.
OL,11,FAssistant Chief Constable Rob Potts,
OL,12,Fwho holds operational responsibility
OL,13,Ffor Counter Terrorism Policing North
OL,14,FWest, said: "Following charging
OL,15,Fauthority being granted by the CPS,
OL,16,Fthis morning we have charged Mohammad
OL,17,FAsim Bashir with a number of terrorism
OL,18,Foffences, including preparation for
OL,19,Facts of terrorism.
OL,26,@vD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
