PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1764933450
OL,3,CMan charged with assisting synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker on earlier reconnaissance
OL,6,F"These charges aren't directly linked
OL,7,Fto the terrorist attack which took
OL,8,Fplace at the Heaton Park Hebrew
OL,9,FCongregation Synagogue but have come
OL,10,Fas a result of enquiries conducted by
OL,11,Four investigation team.
OL,13,F"Bashir has been released without
OL,14,Fcharge in relation to the terrorist
OL,15,Fattack. However, he has been remanded
OL,16,Fin custody to appear at Westminster
OL,17,FMagistrates Court tomorrow to face the
OL,18,Fcharges authorised today.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
