OL,3,CMan charged with assisting synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker on earlier reconnaissance
OL,6,F"Our investigation into the attack
OL,7,Fremains live and I would continue to
OL,8,Fappeal to anyone with information that
OL,9,Fcould potentially be of assistance to
OL,10,Fplease come forward.
OL,12,F"I would also like to once again thank
OL,13,Fmembers of the community for their
OL,14,Fcontinued patience and support as we
OL,15,Fconduct our enquiries."
